Class World

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    javafx.css.Styleable, javafx.event.EventTarget
    public class World
extends javafx.scene.layout.Pane

    World

    This class extends a base class Pane to set the game world and add/remove children freely.

    The object will create a timer for Actor to implement animations.

    Since:
    20/11/2019
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Pinyuan Feng (scypf1)
